# Contributing to Greenledger  

Thank you for your interest in contributing to **Greenledger**!  

## How to Contribute  
- Fork the repository  
- Create a new branch (`git checkout -b feature-name`)  
- Make your changes  
- Commit (`git commit -m "Description of change"`)  
- Push (`git push origin feature-name`)  
- Open a Pull Request  

## Code of Conduct  
All contributors are expected to follow respectful and inclusive behavior.  

## Reporting Issues  
If you find a bug, open an issue with:  
- A clear title  
- Steps to reproduce  
- Expected behavior
